videos.description: Jarret Doege hits Teo Redding in stride up the middle who is able to shake off a defender and zoom in for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Bowling Green scores on 57-yard pitch-and-catch

videos.description: Shakif Seymour bounces to the outside and crosses the goal line for the touchdown to tie the game.
videos.headline: Toledo answers with 3-yard rushing TD

videos.description: Shakif Seymour pounds it into the end zone for the second time in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Seymour scores second rushing TD in first quarter

videos.description: Falcons' Jarret Doege throws a perfect lob pass to Andrew Clair up the middle for the 24-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Doege tosses 2nd TD of first half

videos.description: Toledo's Shakif Seymour finds the end zone for the third time in the first half on a 10-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Seymour has a hat trick of rushing TDs

videos.description: Bowling Green's Jarret Doege finds Teo Redding in the end zone for the touchdown and his 3rd touchdown pass of the first half.
videos.headline: Doege has 3 TD passes before half

videos.description: Shakif Seymour is taking care of business against Bowling Green with his 4th touchdown run in the game.
videos.headline: Seymour adds 4th rushing TD

videos.description: Logan Woodside throws his 86th career touchdown for Toledo which sets a school record.
videos.headline: Woodside throws record-breaking TD

videos.description: Jarret Doege has trouble with the snap, but collects himself and finds a wide-open Scott Miller who is able to walk into the end zone for the score.
videos.headline: Doege taking care of business with 4 TD passes

videos.description: Shakif Seymour rushes in his 5th touchdown becoming the first Toledo running back to do so since NFL star Kareem Hunt.
videos.headline: Seymour trots in for 5th rushing TD

videos.description: Logan Woodside throws a perfect pass along the sideline that finds the outstretched arms of Diontae Johnson who hauls in the pass and scores another Rockets touchdown.
videos.headline: Woodside drops in a dime for another TD
